ivery system of azathioprine. <i>Drug development and industrial pharmacy</i> 39(11) 1765–1773. DOI:<a href=&quot;https://doi.org/10.3109/03639045.2012.736517&quot;>10.3109/03639045.2012.736517</a>  PUBMED:<a href=&quot;https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23110370/&quot;>https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23110370</a></p></li></ol></body></html>",
